      "layout": "The page model is primarily a max-width contained layout of 1320px, with occasional full-bleed sections, especially for heroes. The hero pattern is often a full-viewport dynamic video or large image with a centered, bold headline. Sections alternate between light and cream backgrounds, creating a clear vertical rhythm. Content often uses 2-column layouts with text and visuals, but also features centered stacks for impactful messages. There are instances of 3-column card grids for features or articles. Overall density is comfortable, with generous breathing room between sections. Navigation is a sticky top bar with a left-aligned hamburger menu, a center-aligned logo, and right-aligned ghost buttons.",
      "imagery": "Imagery predominantly features dynamic, high-motion photography, often showcasing drones or expansive natural landscapes from a unique perspective, reinforcing the theme of flight and speed. There's also some use of tightly-cropped product photography or candid lifestyle shots, often integrated directly into text blocks. Visuals are full-bleed for hero sections or contained within organic, wave-like masks. When present, icons are minimalist, outlined, and monochromatic, primarily in Midnight Ink.",
